{remember: [Plant_Name] - [Description_of_plant]. LOCATION: [Environment_type_and_specific_location_where_found]. HARVESTING: [Methods_safety_requirements_and_timing]. USES (GOOD): [Beneficial_applications_and_effects]. USES (BAD): [Harmful_uses_dangers_and_side_effects]. PREPARATION: [Correct_processing_methods_and_timing]. INCORRECT PREPARATION: [Consequences_of_improper_handling_including_transformations].}

