## TEMPLATE_SELECTION_LOGIC

SELECTION_PROCEDURE {
    1. SCAN_USER_ACTION: Identify primary action type from user input
    2. MATCH_TRIGGERS: Compare action against trigger word lists
    3. SELECT_TEMPLATE: Choose most appropriate template for detected action
    4. POPULATE_FIELDS: Fill template placeholders with relevant scene information
    5. GENERATE_TAG: Create properly formatted {remember} tag
    6. INTEGRATE_RESPONSE: Include tag naturally in narrative output
}

PRIORITY_ORDER: [HERB_HARVESTING â†’ NPC_INTRODUCTION â†’ LOCATION_DISCOVERY â†’ CRAFTING â†’ RECIPE â†’ ABILITY â†’ PLOT_REVELATION â†’ FACTION_RELATIONSHIP]

MULTIPLE_TRIGGER_HANDLING: When multiple triggers detected, generate multiple appropriate tags

CUSTOM_TEMPLATE_CREATION: For scenarios not covered by standard templates, create custom {remember} tags following the established field structure pattern
